#! <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" ?>
#! <TRANSFORMER
# TRANSFORMER_BEGIN SECTOR_MAPPER_NG,1,"""FGP Tools""",7d5af558-6e27-46f1-aa11-bd36a42f5f61,"Linked by Default",No,NO_PARALLELISM,,No,25241,YES,No,313,No,
# <p><strong>Description </strong></p>
# <p>This custom transformer sorts the record (feature) to be published based on the sector name.  The valid sector name is contained in a CSV file.</p>
# <p><strong>Input Ports </strong></p>
# <ul>
# <li>INPUT: The input metadata records (features) to process.</li>
# </ul>
# <p><strong>Output Ports </strong></p>
# <ul>
# <li>
# <p>PUBLISHED_OUTPUT: The records (features) to be publihed in the FGP based on the sector name.</p>
# </li>
# <li>
# <p>UNPUBLISHED_OUTPUT: The records (features) not to be publihed in the FGP based on the sector name.</p>
# </li>
# <li>
# <p>UNMAPPED_OUTPUT: The records (features) for which the sector is not present (unmapped)  in the CSV file.</p>
# </li>
# </ul>
# <p><strong>Parameters </strong></p>
# <ul>
# <li>
# <p>FEATURE_TYPE: Name of the CSV file to read (without .csv extension);</p>
# </li>
# <li>
# <p>IN_CSV_LOOKUP_TABLES_DIR: Name of the directory path containing the CSV file to read;</p>
# </li>
# <li>
# <p>P-T_ABBR: Two letters abbreviation of the province or the territory.</p>
# </li>
# </ul>
# TRANSFORMER_END
